OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' as London is used as
OL,4,C'marketplace' for weapon traders
OL,6,FSadiq Khan said he was appalled that
OL,7,Fone of the world's biggest arms and
OL,8,Fdefence trade shows was being held in
OL,9,FLondon - a city home to many who have
OL,10,Ffled conflict.
OL,12,FThe event brings together governments,
OL,13,Farmed forces, and industry leaders
OL,14,Ffrom around the world representing
OL,15,Fdozens of countries.
OL,17,FHeld at London's ExCel Centre in
OL,18,FDocklands the Defence and Security
OL,19,FEquipment International (DSEI) arms
OL,20,Ffair showcases new technologies and
OL,21,Faims to strike international deals.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/7
