OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' as London is used as
OL,4,C'marketplace' for weapon traders
OL,6,FBut London's mayor urged bosses at the
OL,7,FExCel to think twice before staging
OL,8,Fthe event again, adding: "The Mayor is
OL,9,Fcompletely opposed to this event
OL,10,Ftaking place in London and is appalled
OL,11,Fthat the capital is being used as a
OL,12,Fmarketplace for those who wish to
OL,13,Ftrade in weapons.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/7
