OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' as London is used as
OL,4,C'marketplace' for weapon traders
OL,6,F"The Mayor has previously written to
OL,7,Fboth the organisers and ExCel, to
OL,8,Fremind them that London is home to
OL,9,Fthousands of people who have fled
OL,10,Fconflict and suffered as a result of
OL,11,Fweapons like those exhibited at this
OL,12,Fevent, and continues to urge them to
OL,13,Freconsider hosting the fair in London
OL,14,Fin the future."
OL,16,FCritics dismissed Mr Khan's comments
OL,17,Fas "naive" and described him as a
OL,18,F"stuck record".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
