OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' as London is used as
OL,4,C'marketplace' for weapon traders
OL,6,FDefence analyst Francis Tusa said:
OL,7,F"It's two years after the last show,
OL,8,Fhe said pretty much the same thing
OL,9,Flast time.
OL,11,F"So it's a stuck record, a bit of
OL,12,Fstudent politicking. Not very serious.
OL,14,F"I think he's showing his naivety.
OL,16,F"If he talks about refugees and wars
OL,17,Fhe should go and speak to some of the
OL,18,FUkrainian refugees who are in London
OL,19,Fand ask them whether we should be
OL,20,Fspending more on defence equipment,
OL,21,Fespecially to provide to Ukraine.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/7
