OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' as London is used as
OL,4,C'marketplace' for weapon traders
OL,6,F"I think he will get a very robust
OL,7,Fanswer."
OL,9,FMr Tusa said the arms fair was an
OL,10,Fimportant event where the armed
OL,11,Fservices can see what they buy.
OL,13,F"It is very, very important. Is it
OL,14,Falso a showcase for British defence
OL,15,Fcompanies to show other armed forces,
OL,16,FEuropean, American, what we can do and
OL,17,Fsell them," he explained.
