OL,3,CMayor 'appalled' as London is used as
OL,4,C'marketplace' for weapon traders
OL,6,F"And we should bear in mind, in the
OL,7,Flast few days, we've had the
OL,8,Fannouncement of a #10billion order for
OL,9,Ffrigates for Norway. This is the type
OL,10,Fof event where this marketing goes
OL,11,Fon," he added.
OL,13,FThis year's theme, Preparing the
OL,14,FFuture Force, focuses on how defence
OL,15,Forganisations can adapt to new
OL,16,Fchallenges, from digital
OL,17,Ftransformation and artificial
OL,18,Fintelligence to supply chain
OL,19,Fresilience and workforce development.
